data.description: If you are looking for the perfect home to settle in and a great location to access all of what The American Dream City has to offer, then look no further! Welcome to a low maintenance , easy living home. This home has been recently upgraded with luxury vinyl floors and is move-in ready!  A snap shot of features include a covered patio, with 4 spacious rooms , 2 full size baths, and a wood burning fireplace,  The spacious floorplan and outdoor living area are perfect for entertaining guests. Its located in the southern side of the City of Arlington and the quiet outskirts of Mansfield, Texas.  This Eden Rd. Estates home is conveniently close to restaurants, shopping, hiking, biking and fishing with Red Kane Park across the street and the Parks Mall minutes away.  It allows plenty of room to work, rest and relax. Flanked by fantastic neighbors, this NON-HOA is move in ready.  Stop by to Turn the Key!Solar Panels convey in price with acceptable offer!
